text: Helge Werner (23 October 1883 - 6 February 1953) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1953 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Värmland
